name: SOLLOG NFT Eye of Ra Egyptian Pop Art 100 Editions
description:
SOLLOG NFT Eye of Ra Egyptian Pop Art 100 Editions

There are 100 of this NFT that are minted and will be sold 1 by 1, allowing SOLLOG fans to get into the project at an early low price.

Each sale of this series increases the next sale by 1000 XTZ, starting with the first copy at 1000 XTZ, so by the 100th or last copy, the value will be 100,000 XTZ, this allows fans to get in early and make a lot of money as the series sells out.

This is the fairest distribution model SOLLOG can think of due to his popularity.

This is a high resolution 300dip file that can be printed on a museum canvas by the Giclee process or you can display on a high resolution monitor in your home or office

SOLLOG is a listed artist in museums, his site SOLLOG.com is one of the busiest in the world

SOLLOG has the record for sales price of an oil painting at over $1 Billion USD

This NFT is a great investment since SOLLOG is a historic figure who is world famous for his Prophecies
